	"description": "As a web developer, there is a high probability that you have encountered the\ntwo enemies of this article: images and deadlines. Sometimes, for some reasons,\nyour images won’t fit the layout and you don’t want to wrap your head around\nthis for hours.\n\nThis situation has happened to me many times and I have learned from my\nmistakes. No more black magic hacks — here are my five favorites techniques to\nhandle image resizing.\n\nthe “OMG I NEED THIS ASAP” way\nIt’s 5:00 pm on Friday, you have to finish",
